            <ab>To Aminias, one of the diadochoi, hipparches and epistates of Oxyrhyncha, from the Crown cultivators of the said village. Whereas we were formerly 140 men but because of the injustices done to us are 40 in all, although ... (Here the papyrus breaks off.)</ab>
